title: Beast World Crazy Concubine
alternative_titles: 兽世狂妃：不当异界女海王
The Wild Consort of the Beast Realm
The World Of Beasts: I'm Not The King Of The Sea
summary: Beast World Crazy Concubine Manhua Ji Mo crosses over to the orc continent, where there are handsome male beasts wearing beast skins and showing their long legs that can fly, and she became the most adored female in the entire orc continent, and every male wants Ji Mo to have their cubs. “No! Let go of me, you guys! It’s not my ambition to lie around and have cubs every day! ” cried Ji Mo as she struggled in the arms of the handsome male beast.
